                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-58-off291 t17880227-58-cd292"></join>, eight yards of printed cotton, value 18 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880227-58-victim655" type="victimName">
